core_terms/definition.iso_terms/639_3_eng: Record unique identifier across all collections in a database

core_terms/description.iso_terms/639_3_eng: The *document handle* is the record unique identifier in [ArangoDB](https://www.arangodb.com), the default database for this data dictionary. This value is automatically created when a record is inserted, it cannot be modified or set by users and it has the following format: `<collection name>/<_key value>`.

The *document revision* is the record revision number in [ArangoDB](https://www.arangodb.com), the default database for this data dictionary. This value is *fully managed* by the *database* and the user can only *read* its value.

core_terms/definition.iso_terms/639_3_eng: The unique identifier of the document within its collection.

core_terms/description.iso_terms/639_3_eng: The *document key* is the *record* *unique identifier* *within* a *collection* in [ArangoDB](https://www.arangodb.com), the default database for this data dictionary. It is a string that can either be provided by the user, or, if omitted, will be automatically generated by the database.

core_terms/definition.iso_terms/639_3_eng: Reference to the node that represents the origin in a directed graph edge.

core_terms/description.iso_terms/639_3_eng: The value represents the record reference to the node that represents the origin of a relationship in a graph. In [ArangoDB](https://www.arangodb.com) the value is the [_id](https://www.arangodb.com/docs/stable/getting-started-databases-collections-documents.html) of the directed graph relationship source.

core_terms/definition.iso_terms/639_3_eng: Reference to the node that represents the destination in a directed graph edge.

core_terms/description.iso_terms/639_3_eng: The value represents the record reference to the node that represents the destination of a relationship in a graph. In [ArangoDB](https://www.arangodb.com) the value is the [_id](https://www.arangodb.com/docs/stable/getting-started-databases-collections-documents.html) of the directed graph relationship target.
